    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>From KC Studios,</strong> the creator of KC Chronicles and Crimson, comes Sun's Edge, an Action RPG set in a handcrafted world, featuring souls-like combat and Zelda-like open maps to explore.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slash your way into the Crimson Wilds of Cipactlan, a dangerous land being consumed by corruption. Fight monsters, collect specimens, and explore the world to find the lost Crystal Shards before your world is consumed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123900/extras/9bf29590113dfdb1a4683fb31509d833.avif?t=1771228982\" width=680 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mangrove Madness</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;A shard of the Crystal Skull has fallen into the flooded forest, evil spirits have moved in and are terrorizing the locals! Ranger, help find and destroy the shard and bring peace to the river village!&quot; </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123900/extras/9f6920186571df353c1ded39c7f5b777.poster.avif?t=1771228982\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123900/extras/9f6920186571df353c1ded39c7f5b777.webm?t=1771228982\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123900/extras/9f6920186571df353c1ded39c7f5b777.mp4?t=1771228982\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123900/extras/ae4a03553878dec2497075